'''2015年世界室內袋棍球錦標賽'''是第四屆[[世界室內袋棍球錦標賽|世界室內袋棍球錦標賽]]，於2015年9月18日至27日在[[美国|美国]][[纽约州|纽约州]]奥农达加[[印第安保留地|保留地]]及[[锡拉丘兹_(纽约州)|锡拉丘兹]]进行，东道主为[[易洛魁|易洛魁]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Lacrosse is Coming Home to Onondaga Nation|url=http://filacrosse.com/lacrosse-is-coming-home-to-onondaga-nation/|work=Federation of International Lacrosse|date=2015-04-02|accessdate=2020-08-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201132051/https://filacrosse.com/lacrosse-is-coming-home-to-onondaga-nation/|archivedate=2017-12-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此次比赛共有13支队伍参加，与上届相比增加5支，芬兰、德国、以色列、塞尔维亚、瑞士和土耳其都是第一次参赛<ref name="5 things">{{cite news|last1=Moses|first1=Sarah|title=5 things to know about 2015 World Indoor Lacrosse Championship|url=http://www.syracuse.com/sports/index.ssf/2015/09/5_things_to_know_about_2015_world_indoor_lacrosse_championship.html|accessdate=2017-11-18|work=Syracuse.com|date=2015-09-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831104512/https://www.syracuse.com/sports/index.ssf/2015/09/5_things_to_know_about_2015_world_indoor_lacrosse_championship.html|archivedate=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

加拿大队在决赛中击败东道主易洛魁队，第四次获得世界室內袋棍球錦標賽<ref name="bleacher">{{cite news|last1=Rogers|first1=Daniels|title=World Indoor Lacrosse Championship 2015 Results: Medal Winners and Final Scores|url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2572789-world-indoor-lacrosse-championship-2015-results-medal-winners-and-final-scores|accessdate=2017-11-18|work=Bleacher Report|date=2015-09-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831174608/https://bleacherreport.com/articles/2572789-world-indoor-lacrosse-championship-2015-results-medal-winners-and-final-scores|archivedate=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自室內袋棍球世錦賽創立以來，加拿大隊保持全勝紀錄，未負一場<ref name="IL">{{cite news|title=WILC Highlights: Canada's Indoor Reign Continues|url=http://www.insidelacrosse.com/article/wilc-highlights-canada-s-indoor-reign-continues/33078|accessdate=2017-11-18|work=Inside Lacrosse|date=2015-09-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831141313/https://www.insidelacrosse.com/article/wilc-highlights-canada-s-indoor-reign-continues/33078|archivedate=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

铜牌赛中，美国队击败首次参赛的以色列队，第四度获得室內袋棍球世錦賽銅牌<ref>{{cite news|last1=Conwell|first1=Ryan|title=Team USA Settles With Bronze, Defeats Israel 15-4|url=https://laxallstars.com/team-usa-settles-with-bronze-defeats-israel-15-4/|accessdate=2017-11-19|work=Lacrosse All Stars|date=2015-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831072207/https://laxallstars.com/team-usa-settles-with-bronze-defeats-israel-15-4/|archivedate=2018-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

